{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Code Me, dsewnr","author":"dsewnr"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"0d36c900-6062-5be1-82a2-fdd66f2d15fa","excerpt":"Do you know PyCon Japan? (上面是這次 PyCon 梗) 人生第一次參加 PyCon 這次我們訂了中研院內的住宿，CP 值非常高，而且會場就在隔壁而已，讚爆！ 中研院的硬體設施超棒的，研討會辦在中研院真的是太讚了，中研院是個好地方啊！ PyCon 跟目前參加過的 con…","html":"<p><strong>Do you know PyCon Japan?</strong></p>\n<!--more-->\n<p>(上面是這次 PyCon 梗)</p>\n<hr>\n<p>人生第一次參加 PyCon</p>\n<p>這次我們訂了中研院內的住宿，CP 值非常高，而且會場就在隔壁而已，讚爆！</p>\n<p>中研院的硬體設施超棒的，研討會辦在中研院真的是太讚了，中研院是個好地方啊！</p>\n<p>PyCon 跟目前參加過的 con 比，有好多國外的與會者跟講者，也蠻多之前沒看過的贊助商。</p>\n<h3>報到領到的資料</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7abd9d48745818e2d8a9278bdb1dc1c0/7b3f7/pycon-taiwan-2019-0.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pycon taiwan 2019 0\"\n        title=\"pycon taiwan 2019 0\"\n        src=\"/static/7abd9d48745818e2d8a9278bdb1dc1c0/55071/pycon-taiwan-2019-0.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7abd9d48745818e2d8a9278bdb1dc1c0/493b1/pycon-taiwan-2019-0.jpg 163w,\n/static/7abd9d48745818e2d8a9278bdb1dc1c0/17f95/pycon-taiwan-2019-0.jpg 325w,\n/static/7abd9d48745818e2d8a9278bdb1dc1c0/55071/pycon-taiwan-2019-0.jpg 650w,\n/static/7abd9d48745818e2d8a9278bdb1dc1c0/7b3f7/pycon-taiwan-2019-0.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>有質感的硬卡</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; displ